Enable Advanced Currency Management
Setup --> Company Information --> Currency Setup --> Advanced Currency Management (Enable) --> Confirmation that appears : Yes, I want to enable Advanced Currency Management (Checked) --> Enable
Manage Dated Exchange Rates --> Continue --> New Exchange Rates --> 
                                                                      Start Date: (first day of next month)
                                                                      Euro: 1.13
--> Save
===============================================================================================================================================================================================================
Edit the Euro Currency Test Opportunity
App Launcher --> Sales --> Opportunities --> Euro Currency Test --> Details --> Edit --> Change the Close Date to the first date of next month --> Save.
===============================================================================================================================================================================================================
